1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=Saat Aku Bertemu Denganmu=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episod 7=

3
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:20,120
Chu Yunchang, awak ditangkap.

4
00:00:21,559 --> 00:00:22,120
Ayah?

5
00:00:22,239 --> 00:00:24,120
Tunggu, apa maksud semua ini?

6
00:00:24,559 --> 00:00:25,199
Buyu.

7
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:28,239
Dia Jade Squirrel,
Ketua Aliran Sacred Hand Sect.

8
00:00:32,679 --> 00:00:33,640
Apa bukti kamu?

9
00:00:33,799 --> 00:00:35,240
Lady Thousand-Hands, Lin Xin'er,

10
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:37,079
kenal pasti dia sendiri dari penjara.

11
00:00:37,719 --> 00:00:39,759
Aku pun tak kenal Lin Xin'er.

12
00:00:40,079 --> 00:00:40,719
Buyu.

13
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:43,039
Aku sendiri boleh jadi saksi.

14
00:00:43,679 --> 00:00:45,119
Lin Xin'er menamakan dia.

15
00:00:45,479 --> 00:00:46,200
Memang dia.

16
00:00:50,079 --> 00:00:50,759
Buyu.

17
00:00:52,359 --> 00:00:54,079
Kamu cuba lindungi Chu Yunchang?

18
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:55,519
Wushuang.

19
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:58,290
Kamu betul-betul nampak
Jade Squirrel malam tadi?

20
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:00,560
Kamu pasti itu Yunchang?

21
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,479
Apa yang kamu cuba maksudkan?

22
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:07,200
Chang cedera selamatkan adik aku

23
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,519
dan belum pulih lagi.

24
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,760
Luka dia terbuka semula hari ini.
Dia hampir mati.

25
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,840
Adik aku juga cakap

26
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:16,159
Chang berada di sini sepanjang malam.

27
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,359
Dia tak pergi walau sesaat.

28
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,000
Kalau kamu betul-betul nampak

29
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,239
Jade Squirrel malam tadi,

30
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,799
jadi mustahil itu Chang.

31
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,760
Sama ada dia atau tidak,

32
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:28,120
kita perlu bawa dia untuk soal siasat.

33
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,519
Buyu.

34
00:01:32,187 --> 00:01:33,746
Wushuang cuma jalankan tugasnya.

35
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:34,761
Bawa dia.

36
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:41,519
Buyu...

37
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:44,120
Tak apa. Aku ikut mereka.

38
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,400
Buyu,

39
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,680
kamu tak boleh melawat dia di penjara.

40
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,640
Jangan campur!

41
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:51,760
Chang cuma suspek,

42
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,519
bukan penjenayah.

43
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,400
Kenapa aku perlu tarik diri?

44
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:53,760
Kamu...

45
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,519
Semua orang tahu hubungan kamu.

46
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,719
Kamu wajib tarik diri.

47
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,000
Rong,

48
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,040
tepat pada masanya.

49
00:01:59,110 --> 00:02:00,480
Kamu jaga Chang malam itu.

50
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,000
Mustahil
dia boleh keluar.

51
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,040
Maaf, Buyu.

52
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:05,319
Aku di bilik Yunchang

53
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:06,280
sepanjang malam,

54
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,000
tapi aku memang tertidur seketika.

55
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,439
Aku tak boleh tolak kemungkinan

56
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,719
dia Jade Squirrel.

57
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,280
Bagus, Rong.

58
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:17,280
Malam tadi, aku suruh Rong
jaga Chu Yunchang,

59
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,199
tapi itu sebenarnya
alasan untuk pantau dia.

60
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:22,000
Sebaliknya,
Rong tidur lena sepanjang malam.

61
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,080
Macam kejadian dulu
di penjara Three-Hand Sect,

62
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,599
dia langsung tak sedar
Chu Yunchang serang Li Wan.

63
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:29,120
Kemudian, kami terserempak
dengan Jade Squirrel

64
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,199
dan sempat mencederakannya.

65
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:33,000
Sekarang, luka lama Chu Yunchang
kebetulan jadi semakin teruk.

66
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:36,039
Kamu betul-betul percaya
ini semua cuma kebetulan?

67
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:37,500
Ada rangkaian bukti yang kukuh?

68
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,479
Keterangan Lin Xin'er
tak cukup untuk kamu?

69
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,680
Aku akan cari bukti yang aku perlukan

70
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,890
untuk buktikan Chang
bukan Jade Squirrel.

71
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,560
Bila aku jumpa nanti, kamu semua

72
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,800
kena minta maaf secara rasmi pada dia.

73
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:48,800
(Yang jujur dan tak makan rasuah)
Mao Buyu!

74
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,199
Kamu betul-betul dah hilang akal!

75
00:02:53,187 --> 00:02:57,725
(Biro Pintu Gerbang, Kementerian Kehakiman)

76
00:02:57,812 --> 00:03:01,200
(Kementerian Kehakiman)

77
00:03:05,050 --> 00:03:06,490
(Kementerian Kehakiman)
Jadi, inilah Biro Pintu Gerbang.

78
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,120
Memang mengagumkan.

79
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:10,960
Sesuai untuk orang setaraf aku.

80
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:14,450
(Kementerian Kehakiman)

81
00:03:15,210 --> 00:03:16,240
Ini kawasan larangan.

82
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,120
Dilarang masuk tanpa kebenaran.

83
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,439
Tanpa kebenaran?

84
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:19,560
Tengok betul-betul, kawan.

85
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,240
Aku masa depan seluruh biro ini.

86
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,790
Aku tak peduli
walau kamu dewa matahari sekali pun.

87
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:26,000
Kurang ajar...

88
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,199
Hei, Saudara.

89
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:30,590
Kamu orang Biro Pintu Gerbang, kan?

90
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,560
Kita semua bersaudara di sini.

91
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:33,360
Nah.

92
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:35,039
Bawa budak-budak tu pergi minum.

93
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,560
Apa, tak cukup?

94
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,560
Tunggu, ada lagi.

95
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,280
Ambil semua.

96
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,360
Tangkap dia.

97
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,439
Kamu!

98
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:46,400
Apa ini?

99
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:48,240
Menceroboh kawasan Biro Pintu Gerbang

100
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,680
dan cuba merasuah seorang konstabel.

101
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,919
Perbuatan kamu sangat mencurigakan.

102
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:51,319
Rasuah?

103
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,159
Ini buktinya.

104
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,560
Rampas dan soal siasat dia.

105
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,319
Baik, Konstabel Mao.

106
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:55,800
Kamu tahu tak siapa aku?

107
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,159
Jalan.

108
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:57,039
Bagus, budak.

109
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,520
Aku akan ingat muka kau.

110
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,479
(Biro Pintu Gerbang, Kementerian Kehakiman)
Aku Tuan Muda...

111
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:00,879
Aduh, jangan kasar dengan aku.

112
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,560
Buyu.

113
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:05,800
Squire Mei.

114
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,000
Teh tuan.

115
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:14,039
Kamu pun tahu,
Chang lemah dan tak berdaya.

116
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:16,959
Macam mana mungkin dia
Jade Squirrel?

117
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,199
Kecuali kalau

118
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:21,240
kita boleh buktikan Queen Thief of the South
berbohong.

119
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,519
Itu yang susah.

120
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,519
Lin Xin'er dah ditangkap.

121
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:29,839
Mestilah dia
nak heret Chang sekali.

122
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,399
Kenapa kamu cakap begitu?

123
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,000
Begini, dulu

124
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,959
(Xiangming Tea House)
keluarga kami pernah

125
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,199
berurusan dalam perniagaan dengan keluarga Lin.

126
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,720
Mula-mula nampak
semuanya baik saja,

127
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,839
tapi lama-lama kami sedar

128
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,439
rupa-rupanya mereka
keluarga pencuri.

129
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,839
Jadi, ayah mentua aku

130
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:47,240
melaporkan mereka kepada pihak berkuasa.

131
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:50,360
Elder Chu memang berhak buat begitu.

132
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,120
Mungkin betul, tapi...

133
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:54,160
Tapi sebab itu,

134
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,639
dia jadi musuh keluarga Lin.

135
00:04:57,890 --> 00:04:58,800
Kalaulah kita boleh buktikan

136
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,690
Lin Xin'er
memfitnah Chang kerana dendam...

137
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:03,160
Tapi malangnya, tak ada bukti.

138
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,120
Terima kasih atas maklumat itu.

139
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,480
Tentang buktinya,

140
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,839
aku akan cari jalan.

141
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,439
Aku harap pada kamu, Buyu.

142
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:45,519
Chang.

143
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,199
Aku tak patut datang sini.

144
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,079
Tapi malam ni aku terpaksa menyelinap.

145
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:54,639
Cepat.

146
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:57,480
Chang.

147
00:05:57,580 --> 00:05:58,759
Tempat ni sejuk dan lembap.

148
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,600
Tak baik untuk pemulihan.

149
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,439
Jadi aku bawa selimut tambahan untuk kau.

150
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:02,959
Nah.

151
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,360
Cuba pakai ni.

152
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:09,839
Aku tak apa-apa, jangan risau pasal aku.

153
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,079
Duduk.

154
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,759
Aku cuma tak faham

155
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,160
kenapa Lin Xin’er

156
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,480
sanggup sejauh ni nak perangkap aku.

157
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,639
Nampaknya leluhur dia

158
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,639
pernah bermusuhan dengan datuk kau.

159
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,399
Jangan risau. Aku akan terus siasat.

160
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:33,839
Buyu.

161
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,720
Kau kena percaya aku.

162
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,639
Aku tak pernah buat apa-apa

163
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:39,000
untuk sakiti orang tak bersalah.

164
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:40,360
Aku percaya kau.

165
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,000
Fokus saja untuk sembuh.

166
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,879
Yang lain serahkan pada aku.

167
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,079
Cuma...

168
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,000
ada satu benda yang aku tak faham.

169
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,079
Kenapa Lin Xin’er menuduh kau

170
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,720
daripada semua orang?

171
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,580
Kalau ni cuma dendam peribadi,

172
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,519
dia sepatutnya tahu

173
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:06,079
betapa mudah tuduhan palsu itu dipatahkan.

174
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:09,079
Takkan dia sebodoh itu.

175
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:11,981
Mana aku tahu?

176
00:07:12,437 --> 00:07:13,517
Mungkin...

177
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,800
Mungkin dia dah tak waras.

178
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:21,879
Chang.

179
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:24,319
Kau kenal Jade Squirrel?

180
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,360
Kenapa kau tanya aku macam tu?

181
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,879
Jelas aku tak percaya kau orangnya.

182
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:35,480
Tapi kalau kau, atau keluarga kau,

183
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,040
pernah berhutang budi pada dia,

184
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,959
dan sebab setia,

185
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,720
kau lindungi dia...

186
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,240
Tolong, beritahu aku yang sebenar.

187
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,319
Tak ada benda macam tu.

188
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:51,120
Keluarga aku langsung tak ada kaitan

189
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,839
dengan dunia jenayah.

190
00:07:54,725 --> 00:07:56,759
Sama ada Jade Squirrel wira

191
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,959
atau penjenayah biasa,

192
00:07:58,399 --> 00:07:59,160
di sisi undang-undang,

193
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,800
tak ada tempat untuk perasaan peribadi.

194
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,360
Chang,

195
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:03,879
kau mesti beritahu aku kalau kau

196
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,879
dalam keadaan serba salah.

197
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:07,160
Aku akan lindungi kau, apa pun jadi.

198
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,525
Kalau...

199
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,720
Secara andaian saja.

200
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:18,839
Kalau aku memang Jade Squirrel?

201
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:22,040
Apa kau akan buat?

202
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:32,919
Aku rasa...

203
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,559
kau tentu ada sebab kau.

204
00:08:37,975 --> 00:08:39,014
Kau akan tangkap aku?

205
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,320
Ya.

206
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,440
Sebab aku konstabel.

207
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:45,879
Tapi aku akan buat sedaya upaya cari bukti

208
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,440
untuk ringankan hukuman kau.

209
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:52,120
Dan kau masih nak kahwin dengan aku?

210
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:53,159
Ya.

211
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:55,679
Walau selama mana pun,

212
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:57,279
aku akan tunggu kau.

213
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:04,440
Kalau aku dihukum mati pula?

214
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,320
Jangan cakap macam tu.

215
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:13,900
Nak lepas macam tu saja?

216
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:15,240
Teruslah bermimpi.

217
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,440
Rehat elok-elok.

218
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,919
Aku akan datang lagi.

219
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:25,039
Datang sebelum malam.

220
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,080
Gelapnya dalam ni.

221
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,080
Aku takut.

222
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,559
Tunggu sini.

223
00:09:39,725 --> 00:09:43,837
♪Memakai topeng menyorokkan hati♪

224
00:09:43,912 --> 00:09:47,462
♪Berlagak dengan senyuman kosong♪

225
00:09:47,875 --> 00:09:51,575
♪Berhadapan, tak siapa mengalah♪

226
00:09:51,875 --> 00:09:55,700
♪Seorang sedingin ais, seorang sepanas api♪

227
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:59,662
♪Cinta sedalam itu, tapi takdir sekejap saja♪

228
00:09:59,862 --> 00:10:03,650
♪Gelora ini tertanam jauh di dalam♪

229
00:10:03,787 --> 00:10:07,575
♪Aku terlalu rindu, aku ingin kembali♪

230
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:11,400
♪Ke detik pertama kita bertemu♪

231
00:10:11,537 --> 00:10:16,125
♪Buang semua obsesi, semata-mata nak bersama kau♪

232
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:16,879
Macam mana?

233
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,360
Sekarang tak segelap tadi.

234
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,512
♪Aku tak mampu merungkai simpul di hatimu♪

235
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:23,799
Malam ni, aku pinjam sedikit cahaya bulan

236
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,159
dengan besen ni.

237
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,799
Jangan risau.

238
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,440
Aku akan terus cari bukti

239
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,720
supaya kau bebas.

240
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:35,775
♪Tapi seumur hidup aku akan lindungi kau♪

241
00:10:35,850 --> 00:10:39,600
♪Dusta dan janji, biarlah tinggal di masa lalu♪

242
00:10:39,837 --> 00:10:41,812
♪Mari kembali ke saat pertama kita bertemu♪

243
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,120
Malam ini...

244
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:45,720
malam yang indah.

245
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:34,799
Kau...

246
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:41,879
Kau...

247
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:46,039
Tolong! Pengawal!

248
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,200
Ada sesiapa?

249
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,120
(Jin Dian) Kenapa bising sangat?

250
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:49,559
Ini tengah malam!

251
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,559
Ada orang di sini.

252
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,840
Di sini!

253
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,639
Tak ada sesiapa.

254
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:57,320
Tadi dia ada di sini!

255
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,879
Dia memang dalam sel ni!

256
00:11:58,879 --> 00:12:00,600
Diam, atau kau kena sebat!

257
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,120
Tapi aku...

258
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,960
Di mana Sacred Token?

259
00:12:27,559 --> 00:12:29,720
Macam mana kau boleh masuk sini?

260
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:31,879
Kau tak dengar ke?

261
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:34,600
Ini Seni Alih Ruang Aliran Sacred Hand.

262
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,720
Apa yang kau nak?

263
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,137
Kalau kau tak nak bercakap,

264
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,399
tak apa.

265
00:12:43,975 --> 00:12:47,159
Tapi aku tak boleh jamin botol kecil ni

266
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,679
takkan masuk ke mata kau.

267
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:51,360
Kau...

268
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,600
Kau!

269
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,960
Pengawal! Tolong!

270
00:12:58,320 --> 00:13:00,240
Pengawal! Tolong aku!

271
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,799
Ada orang cuba bunuh aku!

272
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,320
Kau dah hilang akal?

273
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,120
Tak, tak!

274
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:05,399
Dia! Dia yang buat!

275
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:07,519
Siapa?

276
00:13:11,799 --> 00:13:13,240
Dia! Memang dia!

277
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,320
Dia baru cuba bunuh aku!

278
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,750
Dia nak bunuh aku!

279
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:16,461
Dia yang buat!

280
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:21,879
Bangun.

281
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,360
Kau buat apa tadi?

282
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:28,600
Tidur.

283
00:13:34,761 --> 00:13:35,362
Perempuan gila.

284
00:13:35,362 --> 00:13:37,041
Kau cuma menipu dan merepek!

285
00:13:38,279 --> 00:13:39,480
Tak! Jangan pergi!

286
00:13:39,690 --> 00:13:40,799
Aku nak jumpa Konstabel Mao!

287
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:41,679
Konstabel Mao!

288
00:13:41,987 --> 00:13:42,823
Konstabel Mao!

289
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,750
Aku mesti jumpa Konstabel Mao!

290
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,080
Aku perlu jumpa dia!

291
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,120
Tolong!

292
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:48,559
Konstabel Mao!

293
00:13:48,559 --> 00:13:49,519
Akhirnya kau sampai!

294
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:51,610
Konstabel Mao!

295
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,440
Mari sini!

296
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,080
Konstabel Mao!

297
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:54,879
Dengar cakap aku!

298
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,480
Chu Yunchang

299
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,960
guna Seni Alih-Ruang

300
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,679
terus muncul tiba-tiba di sini!

301
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:00,960
Tadi dia di sana, lepas tu di sini pula!

302
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,080
Lepas tu dia bercakap dengan aku.

303
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:02,759
Dia ugut aku!

304
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:04,120
Dia nak bunuh aku!

305
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:07,240
Dia pegang botol kecil,
racun yang tembus jantung!

306
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,559
Sebaik aku pejam mata,

307
00:14:08,559 --> 00:14:09,720
dia cuba titiskan benda tu!

308
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:10,559
Dia nak aku mati.

309
00:14:10,559 --> 00:14:11,200
- Dia serius!
- Baik, baik.

310
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,559
Faham. Bertenang dulu.

311
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,279
Jin Dian.

312
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,000
Periksa dia.

313
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:17,879
Ya.

314
00:14:20,279 --> 00:14:22,600
Dia guna Seni Alih-Ruang
nak bunuh aku!

315
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:25,240
Dia betul-betul nak bunuh aku,
Konstabel Mao!

316
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,399
Kau mesti percaya aku!

317
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,519
Tolong, percaya aku!

318
00:14:28,279 --> 00:14:28,840
Kami dah periksa.

319
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,540
- Ini cuma ubat luka biasa.
- Ya, ya.

320
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,480
Dia cedera teruk.

321
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:33,039
Jadi dia dibenarkan simpan sebotol.

322
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:35,720
Inilah botolnya!

323
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,890
Dia guna botol ini
nak racun mata aku dan bunuh aku!

324
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:40,080
Pulangkan pada dia.

325
00:14:40,559 --> 00:14:41,360
Tak, Konstabel Mao!

326
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,080
Kau mesti percaya aku!

327
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,720
Cukup.

328
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,000
Percaya aku!

329
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,380
- Kau mesti percaya aku!
- Tepi.

330
00:14:49,279 --> 00:14:50,759
Jangan kunci! Jangan kunci!

331
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:54,200
Kau cederakan Mak Cik aku.

332
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:57,919
Kau ingat aku akan
lepaskan kau semudah itu?

333
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:00,759
Kau cederakan Mak Cik aku.

334
00:15:01,330 --> 00:15:06,330
Kau ingat aku akan
lepaskan kau semudah itu?

335
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,190
Yu?

336
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:32,519
Apa kau buat di sini?

337
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,690
Aku dengar kau
soal siasat Lin Xin'er.

338
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,800
Aku nak tengok sendiri.

339
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:39,120
Kes ini libatkan Chu Yunchang.

340
00:15:39,130 --> 00:15:40,240
Kau patut jangan campur tangan.

341
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,080
Jangan risau.

342
00:15:42,519 --> 00:15:44,320
Aku cuma memerhati,
bukan nak campur tangan.

343
00:15:45,399 --> 00:15:46,919
Aku percaya kemampuan kau, Wushuang.

344
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:49,120
Aku tahu kau takkan biar
orang tak bersalah teraniaya.

345
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:51,230
Sudah tentu.

346
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:53,879
Memandangkan ini tentang tunangmu,

347
00:15:54,262 --> 00:15:55,542
aku akan siasat habis-habisan.

348
00:15:58,759 --> 00:15:59,399
Tuanku.

349
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:01,240
Lin Xin'er nampak macam hilang akal.

350
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:04,320
Dia elok saja
sebelum dia ditangkap.

351
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,120
Kenapa tiba-tiba meroyan
lepas dipenjara?

352
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:08,759
Kalau Lin Xin'er memang
tak stabil mental,

353
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,320
maka keterangannya

354
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:11,840
takkan ada nilai, betul tak?

355
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:13,679
Kau cuba lindungi Chu Yunchang?

356
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,000
Macam mana aku nak lindungi dia

357
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,080
sedangkan belum ada keputusan?

358
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:18,000
Jangan lupa kau seorang konstabel.

359
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,919
Sebab aku konstabel,

360
00:16:20,519 --> 00:16:21,360
aku takkan benarkan

361
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:23,320
orang tak bersalah dijebak.

362
00:16:30,062 --> 00:16:33,337
♪Dendam dan sesal bak arak yang kuat♪

363
00:16:33,375 --> 00:16:36,250
♪Teguk saja, lepaskan semuanya♪

364
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:42,468
♪Cawan kosong untuk cinta dan benci♪

365
00:16:43,650 --> 00:16:46,970
♪Air mata kaburkan takdir yang tak mampu ku kawal♪

366
00:16:47,100 --> 00:16:50,020
♪Mari minum sampai fajar♪

367
00:16:51,188 --> 00:16:56,428
♪Di sebalik topeng ini, aku takkan berdusta♪

368
00:16:57,650 --> 00:17:00,043
♪Setiap pertemuan semula terasa seperti pertama kali♪

369
00:17:00,043 --> 00:17:03,693
♪Senyuman tersembunyi ini takkan pudar♪

370
00:17:03,762 --> 00:17:07,252
♪Satu hati, tetap di sisimu♪

371
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:10,325
♪Hingga ke hujung waktu♪

372
00:17:10,325 --> 00:17:13,700
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

373
00:17:13,887 --> 00:17:17,475
♪Diselubungi awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

374
00:17:17,475 --> 00:17:23,715
♪Untuk mencari dirimu
dan pegang janji kita selamanya♪

375
00:17:24,050 --> 00:17:27,265
♪Doa sunyi dalam jiwaku♪

376
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:31,088
♪Mendukung sumpahku di bawah bulan♪

377
00:17:31,375 --> 00:17:34,400
♪Moga kita takkan terpisah lagi♪

378
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:37,500
♪Menuju selamanya♪

379
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:41,350
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

380
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:44,710
♪Diselubungi awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

381
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:50,860
♪Untuk mencari dirimu
dan pegang janji kita selamanya♪

382
00:17:51,937 --> 00:18:01,577
♪Hanya untuk bersamamu♪

